# Atlas Playground — Workers Static Assets exclude list (V1.16 Welle C)
#
# `[assets] directory = "."` in wrangler.toml means the static-asset binding
# scans this whole folder. The .assetsignore file excludes paths we do NOT
# want served as static assets (Worker source, dependencies, dev artefacts,
# repository docs).
#
# Syntax: gitignore-like (one pattern per line, # for comments, leading !
# for negation).

# Worker source tree (served via Worker code, not as static asset)
worker/

# Node dependencies (only present when developing locally)
node_modules/

# Repository / dev artefacts that must never be public
.gitignore
.assetsignore
README.md
wrangler.toml
package.json
package-lock.json
tsconfig.json
*.test.ts
*.test.js

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
